<% af_category "Exterior Signage" do %>
  <p>
    Exterior signage is one of the most important features your company needs. If your business does not have signage it will
    be difficult for customers - both those seeking you out and foot traffic patronage - to find you. There are numerous sign 
    materials to choose from, all at varying price points. Sign materials include, but are not limited to: fabric, illuminated 
    vinyl, painted or carved wood, paint glass storefront, pressed metal. Each of these sign materials offers different installation 
    options as well.
  </p>

  <p>
    When considering sign type it is also recommended that you check your local zoning regulations so that you know any applicable 
    rules like height and width. This can be done by contaction the city hall your business will be located in or simply by Googling 
    your business zipcode + signage zoning regulations.
  </p>
<% end %>

